<sect1 id="keyboard-shortcuts">
<title>Keyboard Shortcuts</title>
<subtitle>Build a better Mouse-trap</subtitle>
<para>While a mouse or other <quote>pointing device</quote> is a wonderful thing the simple fact is that many operations 
on most Graphical User Interfaces can be undertaken much more effectively using  Accelerators  
or Keyboard Shortcuts. While they are not as intuitive for most of us once learned you wonder how you lived without them.</para>
<para>&app; is no exception to this &lt;pun&gt; rule_ of _thumb &lt;/pun&gt;. </para>
<para>We hope you find the Default Short-Cuts simple to use and remember but by all means take advantage of  <application>GTK</application>
and <link linkend="gtk-tips-features">Roll Your Own</link>.</para>


